{
  "stem": "24544.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the Silesia, I think, [NON-ENGLISH], Herr Bader-- we just called him yellow officer, because he has a yellow uniform.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Friedrich, who was with the potato cleaning, was the grey officer-- we didn't know their name-- came over there, and he saw me to working.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know the German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Work is the most important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He saw me to work and came over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know German-- a little from school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe somebody translated, or not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He asked me why I am home if I could work like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I said, I have trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, show me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So again, open up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Lift up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he himself took me in the ambulance, or emergency, or hospital, whatever, another big [NON-ENGLISH], like the [NON-ENGLISH] exactly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were people on straw, lying down, half dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think a barber came every week, once.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He once, I saw-- I saw-- cut over the ankle somebody's leg, because it was frozen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No anesthesia, no frozen, nothing, just a sharp knife, he cut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he put on some gaze.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From paper.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Paper.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what that yellow officer did, he took me before everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two, three girls was over there, who took care of the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he asked them to put some cream on me and put me heavy, heavy paper, gaze, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't gaze, it was from paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was packed up, bandaged up, with a whole day's gaze, which could be go for everybody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not so long time after that, two hours later, the gray guy came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I think they wanted to see a woman, a normal body of a woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the meantime, I run in the ambulance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They took off the gaze from me, just left a little, little.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
